# ovh_vps_snapshot_revert

Reverts an OVHcloud VPS to its current snapshot.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/resources/vps_snapshot_revert/example_1.tf"}}

## Argument Reference

The following arguments are supported:

* `service_name` - (Required) The service_name of your VPS.

## Attributes Reference

(See generated docs/resources/vps_snapshot_revert.md for the full attribute list.)

